      "beast_baseline": "the warmth of the coffee doesnt change anything though. it's just a ritual for a life that isn't mine anymore. i feel like i'm just going through the motions of a person who died along with him. there's no future to look forward to, just more days of sitting in this emptiness. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever will.",
      "beast_suffix": "",
